Full adder sum: x XOR y XOR z
& negation: -(x XOR y XOR z)
x XOR y = (x+y)(-x + -y) = [[x, y], [-x, -y]]
-(x XOR y) = (x+ -y)(-x + y) = [[x, -y], [-x, y]]

(x XOR y) XOR z = ((x XOR y) + z)(-(x XOR y) + -z)
= ((x+y)(-x + -y) + z) ((x+ -y)(-x + y) + -z)
= ((x+y+z)(-x + -y +z)) ((x+ -y + -z)(-x + y + -z))

= (x+y+z) (-x + -y + z) (x + -y + -z) (-x + y + -z)
...
= -x-yz + -xy-z + xyz + x-y-z
